flowRoot.flowPara: Where are you? This is the landing page of the FarmStall API (v1 ).It is a made-up API that complements a book that we're writing. You can go check out the book over here, its currently in the Manning Early Access Program ( or MEAP ).

Designing APIs with Swagger and OpenAPI teaches you how to work with OpenAPI as a platform for working with RESTful APIs. Using Swagger tools and best practices. It's currently in early release with several chapters ready.
